 years of experience in implementing both tier 1 and tier 2 ERP systems, including SAP, Oracle, Microsoft Dynamics, SAGE, and Netsuite ERPs. Our IT advisors can offer functional, technical system integration and program management knowledge to empower businesses to use these applications successfully.\n<br>\n<br>\nOur team offers ERP implementation and deployment to automate business functions and processes, including:		\n			<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/css/widget-icon-list.min.css\">		<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Financial Management.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Human Capital Management.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Business Intelligence and Reporting.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Manufacturing and Production.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Supply Chain Management.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Procurement and Sourcing.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Project Management and Accounting.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Sales and Marketing.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Service Management.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n		<p>BlueAngle not only works with clients for ERP implementation, but our experienced IT advisors help analyze current business needs and upcoming trends to select, design and plan for implementation as well. We work to accommodate any additional training, maintenance, and launch needs to ensure the transition takes place smoothly.</p>		\n													<img width=\"530\" height=\"435\" src=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1-1.jpg 530w, https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1-1-300x246.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" />													\n													<img width=\"530\" height=\"510\" src=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-1-1.jpg 530w, https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-1-1-300x289.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" />													\n			<h1>Software Development & Application Customization</h1>		\n		<p>We aim to help each client rapidly automate their business processes. Therefore, our IT consultants will review your current processes, look at existing applications, and recommend, design, and deploy the appropriate software to maximize cost-effectiveness, increase productivity, and help keep your business a step ahead of the competition.</p><p>Realistically, cutting edge performance requires cutting edge software. That’s why BlueAngle offers custom software development to meet your business needs. We work diligently to develop software that integrates industry best practices and utilizes new technologies. We utilize the following five key elements when creating software for our clients:</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										A passion for great design, innovation, and new technology.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Our creativity and adaptability to your business needs.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Our industry experience.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										A strong focus on your underlying business goals.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Ongoing support and maintenance to keep your software running smoothly.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n		<p>We’ve developed a variety of software applications for clients across multiple industries. Additionally, we have experience in customizing pre-existing software to better meet our client’s business needs.</p>		\n													<img width=\"530\" height=\"525\" src=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3.jpg 530w, https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3-300x297.jpg 300w, https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" />													\n			<h1>Application Integration</h1>		\n		<p>Full application integration is essential to many clients. Integrating applications allows all of your programs, including ERPs, commercial software suites, mobile products, customized software, and proprietary BlueAngle technology to work together to provide you with seamless, streamlined business processes. Integrating platforms allows various software applications to communicate and feed data across platforms, eliminating the need for manual data transfer. Ultimately, effective application integration helps save our customers time and money while also improving data accuracy by eliminating the risk of human error.</p><p>BlueAngle’s team of highly-qualified IT consultants have experience working with a wide range of platforms, applications, and middleware, making it easy for us to help our clients integrate almost any commercial, proprietary, or customized application in a way that meets their business needs. Whether our clients need assistance with consolidated business reporting, data analytics, or integrating mobile technologies as delivery methods, BlueAngle’s team works to provide our clients with a single, centralized platform that allows your business to thrive while planning for scalability. Our application integration offerings include but are not limited to:</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Integrating diverse programs and databases.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Master data management.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Correlation of meaningful business information from events and data flows through complex event processing.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										On-going technical and application support.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n		<p>We’ve helped clients with application integration in many fields, including commercial banking, consumer retail, hospitality, and government services. More information on the effectiveness of our application integration can be found in our <a href=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/case-studies/\">case studies</a></p>		\n													<img width=\"530\" height=\"525\" src=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3.jpg 530w, https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3-300x297.jpg 300w, https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" />													\n													<img width=\"530\" height=\"380\" src=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/4-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/4-3.jpg 530w, https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/4-3-300x215.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" />													\n			<h1>BlueAngle Cloud Services</h1>		\n		<p>Many industries benefit from cloud-based application hosting services. At BlueAngle, we have developed and deployed a cloud-based human resource application suite that provides our clients with tools that aid in financial management, reporting and business intelligence, and business analytics. We host these applications in “AngleCloud”, our proprietary cloud-based environment. Using AngleCloud comes with many benefits for our clients, including:</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Eliminating one-time-only and capital costs associated with commercial software and hardware setup.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Easy access to critical information with minimal upfront costs, including pay-as-you-go monthly payment options and on-demand requests.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Accelerated application implementation based on our organization’s complexity.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Quick and interim fix solutions to keep your business running and eliminate downtime due to system issues through cloud applications.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Access to the most recent software and real-time updates, hotfixes, patches, and more for each of our proprietary applications.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Scalability solutions without the need to repurchase expensive software licenses.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n													<img width=\"530\" height=\"270\" src=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/5-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/5-1.jpg 530w, https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/5-1-300x153.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" />													\n			<h1>Mobile Applications</h1>		\n		<p>At BlueAngle, we understand how important it is to our clients to have access to critical information while on the go. As a result, we offer a variety of applications for mobile devices, including smartphones and tablets, that allow users to get their data when they need it most. We offer support for these applications on Android, iPhone, and Blackberry devices. Some of the features and functionalities our mobile applications provide include:</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Time and Attendances.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Inventory management and bar-code lookup.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Airline ticketing.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										e-Payments for services and goods across multiple industries.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Tracking sales performance, field sales, and real-time metrics.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Real-time reporting.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Business analytics\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n													<img width=\"530\" height=\"270\" src=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/5-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/5-1.jpg 530w, https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/5-1-300x153.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" />													\n													<img width=\"530\" height=\"420\" src=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/imgpsh_fullsize_anim-_1_-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/imgpsh_fullsize_anim-_1_-1.jpg 530w, https://blueangle.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/imgpsh_fullsize_anim-_1_-1-300x238.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\" />													\n			<h1>Application Maintenance & Support</h1>		\n		<p>Support, technical help, and troubleshooting are some of the key pillars of BlueAngle’s client-first service model. We offer periodic updates and patches for our proprietary software as part of our application development packages. Additionally, we help clients tackle the challenges of working in an evolving business landscape by providing additional features and software functionality as needed. Our team also works with clients to provide customer support for commercial software and technology, including troubleshooting and general maintenance on many well-known software packages. Some other ways we provide long-term maintenance and support to our clients include:</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Developing and deploying software upgrades, patches, hotfixes, and more.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Application assessment and audits for architecture, design, and performance.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Application enhancement, including change implementations and functional upgrades for customized software and in-house platforms.\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Problem management and root-cause analysis.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Application performance monitoring and management.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Ongoing application training and upscale training for existing employees.\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Preventative and proactive maintenance and support for software and hardware.\n									</li>\n						</ul>','Business Applications','','publish','c