.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Cost pressures require relentless focus on standardization, consolidation and optimizing service delivery\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Rapidly evolving Infrastructure and Operations strategies are driving new shared services models and requirements\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n			<h2>As part of our delivery model, our infrastructure related services include:</h2>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Data Center Operations (including on-premise and hosted Data Centers)\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Open Systems (including services provided predominantly on Unix/Linux platforms)\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Identity and Security Management\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg>						\n										Network / Telecommunications (Local Area Networks, Wide Area Networks, etc.)\n									</li>\n								<li>\n							<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\